        "content": "<p>In the NNG, if I have <br>\na b c:mynat<br>\nh: b=a+c (or h: b=a+0),<br>\nHow to convert h to a&lt;=b or introduce a new hypothesis a&lt;=b?</p>",
        "id": 239722239,
        "sender_full_name": "Lu-Ming Zhang",
        "timestamp": 1621589624
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you could put <code>have h2 : a &lt;= b</code> and then you'll get a new goal which you can prove using <code>h</code>.</p>",
        "id": 239725848,
        "sender_full_name": "Kevin Buzzard",
        "timestamp": 1621591502
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110038\">Kevin Buzzard</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/113489-new-members/topic/convert.20equality.20to.20inequality/near/239725848\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>you could put <code>have h2 : a &lt;= b</code> and then you'll get a new goal which you can prove using <code>h</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>In the NNG, I put <code>have h2 : a &lt;= b</code>, then I only got <code>h2 : Prop</code>.  Why is that?</p>",
        "id": 239727487,
        "sender_full_name": "Lu-Ming Zhang",
        "timestamp": 1621592393
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>By the way, how to input letters like ℕ in Lean?</p>",
        "id": 239729146,
        "sender_full_name": "Lu-Ming Zhang",
        "timestamp": 1621593306
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It sounds like you wrote <code>have h2 := a &lt;= b</code> not <code>have h2 : a &lt;= b</code>.</p>",
